Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni si!{\alphaFF} Odhoď ten nôž!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni si! Odhoď ten nôž!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Krvácaš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urob, čo ti hovorím. Odhoď ten nôž a otoč sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to zlé... ak sa vzdá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,610)}Nehýbte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu robíte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:32.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty! Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj, lebo budeme strieľať!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,610)}Počkajte. Nestrieľajte. Všetko vám vysvetlím!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo odhoď ten nôž!
