Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.48,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj tréning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}... bude určite veľmi ťažký.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Ale nevzdávaj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Cabbage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Si veľmi milý...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}... nenechávaj sa nikým oklamať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Baremoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... si múdry,...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... jedného dňa sa staneš bohatým.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Joe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:53.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Modlím sa celým srdcom, aby si sa opäť stretol \Nso svojou sestrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Setsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:11.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... šťastný, že som ťa stretol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:26.72,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\an2}Mihnutím oka, niekoľko striel prešlo Sakuragiho telom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.76,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Jediné, o čom vtedy premýšľal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.10,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}... boli jeho priatelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... voľní.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vítajte doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátil som sa, Setsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:06.48,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom som trafil Amerického vojaka\N ľavým hákom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel by som, aby si to videla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to strašné! Po údere ihneď vstal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo so Sakuragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:23.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si o sebe myslíš, An-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsuko-san kvôli tebe plače...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.11,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred tým si sľúbil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.57,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal si, že keď všetci budeme vonku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.88,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.23,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si odišiel sám...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.54,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.09,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Takto sa to nemalo stať...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.09,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:29.30,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Budúci rok, dúfajme, že budeme vonku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:40.38,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Pod stromom, na ktorom sú vyrezané naše sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.67,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Šťastie čakalo na druhej strane sedem \Nfarebného mosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:51.57,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Je potrebné mať odvahu, na prekročenie tohto klzkého\N a nebezpečného mosta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.17,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}An-chan ich to naučil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.30,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.42,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby sme ťa mohli vidieť,...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.66,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,... boli by sme šťastní.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:15.02,RAINBOW Onscreen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,570)\fad(300,300)}6. júna, 1957.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:17.62,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,6 júna, 1957. Sľúbený deň.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetkým sa podarilo dostať von?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoon, čo to máš za účes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pasuje ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drž hubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako Baremoto? No nie je vonkajší vzduch\N osviežujúci?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:00.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabbage! Ty si ešte väčší!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz nám...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... o An-chanovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki bol pri tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:22.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol už veľmi vážne zranený, keď polícia začala strieľať...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to ich práca, Mario?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem podrobnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.47,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On už nie je nažive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chana nám už nič nevráti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chanove posledné želanie bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:56.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby sme nasledovali svoje sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám v úmysle ísť svojou cestou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vy by ste mali, tiež...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... ísť tou svojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som šťastný, že som vás\N mohol vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Držte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je jasné na čo myslíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:31.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš sám zabiť Ishiharu\N a Sasakiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si myslíš, prečo sme sem\N prišli?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň niesť sám to celé veľké\N bremeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urobme to spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baremoto, má určite nejaký dobrý plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechajte to na mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, ale pre začiatok sa niečoho napime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.62,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjedol by som niečo, ihneď!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.32,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.98,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to idioti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:04.27,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj najväčší idioti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.50,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Všetci šiesti mali rovnaké pocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:16.65,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}"Sasaki a Ishihara musia zaplatiť, inak to, že sme vonku\N nemá žiadnu cenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.03,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Pre všetkých začalo veľmi dlhé leto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.07,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Prešli dva mesiace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.79,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier tvrdo trénoval v JSDF (Japonská armáda).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:38.33,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe začal pracovať, ako pomocník v kapele.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neváhaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.73,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabbage pracoval, ako robotník, aby mal každý deň výplatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:50.28,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoon, ako obvykle, \Ntrávil každý deň predajom amerického tovaru\N na čiernom trhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.22,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mario sa zaúčal za barmana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.87,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Každý pracoval, aby nejako vyžil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.18,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}A vtedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:02.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo do...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.27,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.58,RAINBOW Paper Head,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H222C2B&\frz13.5\fs48\pos(576,341)}Hlavný kandidát na primátora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.04,RAINBOW Paper,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H222C2B&\fs36\frz283.461\pos(972,921)}Sasaki Gisuke vedie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voľba starostu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... a on vedie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nežartujte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten prekliaty bastard kandiduje \Nna starostu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajtra,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sa Sasaki zúčastní diskusie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže vtedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uskutočníme náš útok!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho som čakal na tieto slová.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:34.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Začneme tým, že sa rozdelíme do dvoch skupín. \NJedna pôjde na Sasakiho diskusiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dve skupiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo tá druhá?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesto Numazu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je miesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... kde je Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishihara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže tam je ten bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:53.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pošleme ho do pekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ÁNO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovoľte, aby som sa o neho postaral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:20.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V poriadku Mario. Choď a postaraj sa o neho \Nraz a navždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sech-chan, máš hosťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:29.49,RAINBOW Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(640,27)\be1}Nemocnica č. 3 v Marui
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:29.49,RAINBOW Transparent,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\fscx280\fscy300\pos(586,48)}I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostatní sa majú dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Všetci si riadia svoje životy sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.82,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem. To som rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:51.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:53.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem, či to bude stačiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale mám iba toľko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.75,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? To si nemusel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, keby som ti ich nedal teraz, \Nkedy potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.35,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... neviem, kedy by sa ešte naskytla príležitosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.89,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem pozdraviť Ishihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo chceš urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš sa pomstiť za to\N čo urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.97,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chystáš sa ho zabiť, lebo aj on zabíjal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:33.19,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo neskončíš s týmito nezmyslami a nezačneš myslieť\N na svoju budúcnosť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nejde o to Setsuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem napredovať, pokiaľ neurobím niečo \Nhneď teraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:44.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem zabudnúť, čo nám urobili \NIshihara a Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím to vykonať, ako muž.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, Mario-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... niečo také...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.19,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... by Sakuragi-kun nikdy neurobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:21.86,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to jedna guľka z tela Sakuragiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vezmi si ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.63,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, Sakuragi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.00,RAINBOW Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochraňuj ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to robíš? Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ospravedlňte ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nejakí ľudia stoja na ceste...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.12,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.50,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho sme sa nevideli, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viem, že si tam, Sasaki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu robíte? \NChoďte z cesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:24.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho sme sa nevideli! \NUkáž sa, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, je to pravda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uchádzaš sa o úrad starostu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Á-Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:38.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy, odkiaľ poznáte Sasaki-senseia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:44.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viete, keď sme boli v zariadení Shonan, tak sa o nás\N veľmi dobre postaral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:48.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka nemu sme začali nový život!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľa šťastia vo voľbách!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci vás budeme podporovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baremoto... si si istý?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:11.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakajte a pozerajte sa!\N Všetko sa ešte len začína.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čakal som...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si tu, aby si ma zabil, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:41.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:43.52,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále som na teba čakal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:00.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som už unavený...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabi ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.58,RAINBOW Whisper,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:15.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki, ty hajzel! Oklamal si ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:20.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuragi žije a stojí tu predo mnou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslí si, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... ja som...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... Sakuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:30.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby si ma zabil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:35.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ako som sa snažil zabiť ja teba, \Npamätáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedel som to, takže si ho zabil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V niektorých ohľadoch je to smutné, \Nže Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si mohol zabudnúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som nezabudol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:59.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten pocit, keď nôž uviazol v tvojom\N tele bol skvelý!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabi ma pekne a pomaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byť zabitý pomaly, je celkom pekné...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Či nie, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.45,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:43.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo taký úbohý feťák ako ty, sa stal dôvodom, že An-chan umrel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taký...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... úbohý chlap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}... ISHIHARA!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.50,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Musím to vykonať... ako muž.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:08.37,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Nemôžem napredovať, ak ho nechám žiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.85,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Setsuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.93,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Nikdy neodpustím tomu, \Nkto zabil An-chana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.88,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}To je neodpustiteľné.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:34.83,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}An-chan je mŕtvy. Zmizol na druhej \Nstrane dúhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:38.53,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Jeho učenie ostalo v tých\N šiestich chlapcoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:01.99,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Slnko bola jediná vec, \Nktorú som cítil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.67,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Než som sem prišiel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:09.39,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Ale ešte vo svojom vnútri som pociťoval, že pršalo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.03,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}A každá kvapka je naša slza
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:17.49,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Je pravda, že sme sami, ale toto miesto nám niečo dalo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.54,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,A NEJAKO SME SA STALI SILNÝMI!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:28.04,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Je to miesto na stene, kde zásady a sny sa nestratili
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:32.22,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Trváme naďalej stúpať po týchto múroch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.98,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Vždy budeme bojovať
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:43.49,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Je to miesto na stene, kam sa musíme vrátiť späť
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:49.56,RAINBOW OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,150)}Dnešným dňom, v ktorom sme zistili, že nie sme sami
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.40,RAINBOW ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}S prázdnymi pohľadom,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.74,RAINBOW ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}čo mám ďalej hľadať?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:36.32,RAINBOW ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Môžeš sa venovať,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:41.08,RAINBOW ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}životom tých, čo musíme chrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:45.42,RAINBOW ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Vytlačil si ma z miesta,
